						<h4>Chris Duffy</h4>
												<p>CHRIS DUFFY is a stand-up comedian who has worked as a television writer (Wyatt Cenac’s Problem Areas on HBO, National Geographic Explorer) and is currently host of TED’s hit podcast How to Be a Better Human, winner of the 2025 Webby Award for Advice & How-To Podcasts. He has appeared on Good Morning America, ABC News, and NPR.</p>
